  "title": "A round silver UFO spotted by 5 people in Brasília-DF [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/01/a-round-silver-ufo-spotted-by-5-people-in-brasilia-df-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jK",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 13th, 1994</strong>. Time: 04:00 am. Duration: not determined. From the window of her apartment in Asa Sul de Brasília, Distrito Federal, a woman with four other people observed, with the naked eye, an unidentified flying object with a round shape and silver color, flying at low speed. According to witnesses, the UFO was positioned right where &#8220;the Sun [normally is] at 08:00am&#8221; performing vertical and horizontal trajectories.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.385. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado no Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>DEC 13th, 1994. Time: 04:00 am. Duration: not determined. From the window of her apartment in Asa Sul de Brasília, Distrito Federal, a woman with four other people observed, with the naked eye, an unidentified flying object with a round shape and silver color, flying at low speed. According to witnesses, the UFO was positioned [&hellip;]</p>\n",
